### **3Ô∏è‚É£ System Architecture**

**Architecture Type:** *Three-Tier Architecture*

| Layer                  | Description                             | Example                                                  |
| ---------------------- | --------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Presentation Layer** | Handles user interface and interactions | Salesforce Lightning pages / Web UI                      |
| **Application Layer**  | Contains business logic and workflows   | Apex classes, triggers, and validation rules             |
| **Database Layer**     | Stores and manages lease-related data   | Salesforce objects like Property, Tenant, Lease, Payment |

This separation ensures **modularity**, **security**, and **easy maintenance**.

