### **5Ô∏è‚É£ Entity‚ÄìRelationship (ER) Diagram**

**Entities and Attributes:**

| Entity          | Attributes                                                          |
| --------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Tenant**      | Tenant_ID, Name, Email, Phone, Address                              |
| **Property**    | Property_ID, Name, Location, Type                                   |
| **Lease**       | Lease_ID, Start_Date, End_Date, Rent_Amount, Property_ID, Tenant_ID |
